{"tid":2178982,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[Panmenkitchen] 星期六 8點正 30分鐘煮好 簡單日本餐","createTime":"2020-08-28T19:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T13:47:40.000Z","uid":156466,"like":31,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9f15f3d007f1541aaf80a8eb516d927e383035a1","tid":2178982,"uid":156466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開定post預告定 <br />\n雖然知都無乜人睇<br />\n希望有人知先<br />\n同埋我知有小朋友睇<br />\n我會盡量唔講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾次機會<br />\n<br />\n講定煮啲咩今次<br />\n<br />\n日式甜蝦通粉沙律<br />\n青酒牛油煮貝殼<br />\n青酒煮蜆水茶碗蒸<br />\n照燒親子雞扒丼飯<br />\n<br />\n基於之前直播得太耐 <br />\n試下挑戰30分鐘完成 <br />\n希望大家會有興趣睇啲<br />\n都係嗰句 有一個人睇都煮<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果真係有興趣睇 <br />\n不訪大家講下想我點煮 煮啲咩<br />\n<br />\n有野食問題不訪tg 我<br />\ntg:seafoodpeter<br />\nig:panmenkitchen<br />\nfb:panmen Kitchen <br />\n<br />\n聽日放link"},{"pid":"2bba9a055d8f28cf76526f86d8b1c3c8087f2d84","tid":2178982,"uid":1590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T20:28:16.000Z","msg":"首推"},{"pid":"8a33e5caaf1d978be08b3648391a111678b99f1a","tid":2178982,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T20:41:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821c48987c0c7bfa1cad11a1efd1a3e8093376f1","tid":2178982,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T20:42:03.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3458d0e3cb8854731ed9a87d249c7925e0dd53","tid":2178982,"uid":369920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:22:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e8e17cf1b908e2f8b67b68d71a49c93ccdb6684","tid":2178982,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":